# Integration Guide: BridgeVehicleHardware + FlyncDaemon

Generated by `vhal-gen`. This guide works with **any Android 14 VHAL tag** from Gerrit.

## Prerequisites

- AOSP source tree synced with an Android 14 automotive target
- The VHAL source at `hardware/interfaces/automotive/vehicle/aidl/`

## Directory Layout After Integration

```
hardware/interfaces/automotive/vehicle/aidl/impl/
├── vhal/
│   ├── Android.bp                     (MODIFIED: add BridgeVehicleHardware dep)
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── VehicleService.cpp         (REPLACED: uses BridgeVehicleHardware)
│   └── ...
├── bridge/                            (NEW: generated files)
│   ├── Android.bp
│   ├── BridgeVehicleHardware.h
│   ├── BridgeVehicleHardware.cpp
